77
00:03:51,740 --> 00:03:52,690
I get it.

78
00:03:53,140 --> 00:03:54,970
We're going to raise good money.

79
00:04:05,330 --> 00:04:06,209
Yes.

80
00:04:06,210 --> 00:04:07,649
